<div class="page-policy section-padding">
  <div class="page-width page-width--narrow">
    <header class="page-policy__header text-center">
      <h1 class="page-policy__title">Return &amp; Refund Policy</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="page-policy__content">
      
      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <p>We are committed to ensuring your satisfaction with our skin and body care products. Please read our policy carefully:</p>
      </section>

      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <h2 class="page-policy__heading">1. Eligibility for Returns</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Returns are accepted within 7 days from the date of delivery.</li>
          <li>Products must be unused, unopened, and in their original packaging.</li>
          <li>Items that are damaged due to shipping or defective are eligible for replacement or refund.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <h2 class="page-policy__heading">2. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Opened or used products</li>
          <li>Products purchased on sale or promotional offers</li>
          <li>Gift cards or samples</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <h2 class="page-policy__heading">3. Return Process</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To initiate a return, please contact our Customer Support within 7 days of receiving your order.</li>
          <li>Provide your order number, product details, and reason for return.</li>
          <li>Once approved, you will receive instructions on how to return the product.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <h2 class="page-policy__heading">4. Refunds</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Refunds will be processed within 7–10 business days after we receive and inspect the returned product.</li>
          <li>Refunds will be issued to the original payment method used for purchase.</li>
          <li>Shipping charges are non-refundable, except in cases where the product was damaged or incorrect.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <h2 class="page-policy__heading">5. Exchanges</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Exchanges are only possible for defective or damaged products.</li>
          <li>Contact our Customer Support with your order details to request an exchange.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="page-policy__block">
        <h2 class="page-policy__heading">6. Shipping for Returns</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Customers are responsible for the cost of return shipping unless the product was damaged or incorrect.</li>
          <li>We recommend using a trackable shipping service for returns.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .page-policy {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .page-policy__header {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .page-policy__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    color: #2F342C;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .page-policy__date {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #5F715A;
    font-family: var(--font-body-family);
  }
  .page-policy__block {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .page-policy__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: #2F342C;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .page-policy__content p, .page-policy__content ul, .page-policy__content li {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(47, 52, 44, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .page-policy__content ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }
  .page-policy__content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .page-policy__content a {
    color: #5F715A;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .page-policy__content a:hover {
    color: #2F342C;
  }
  
  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-policy {
      padding: 5rem 0;
    }
    .page-policy__header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .page-policy__block {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Return Policy",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
